Dialogue: 2,0:28:26.60,0:28:30.22,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}go to RedHat.com/CommandLineHeroes.
Dialogue: 3,0:28:30.50,0:28:33.52,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在那里你也可以注册我们的新闻通讯
Dialogue: 2,0:28:30.50,0:28:33.52,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Once you're there you can also sign up for our newsletter.
